data.description: *Seller Offering $10k Credit to buyer with Full Price Offer* Welcome to this beautifully maintained 3 bedroom + office/den, 2 bath rambler located in the Delphi Golf Course neighborhood.  Featuring an open concept kitchen with quartz countertops, an eat at island, pantry, and stainless steel appliances.  Get cozy by the fireplace in the spacious living area.  Laminate flooring throughout main living/kitchen area.  The primary has an attached bath and a large walk in closet.  The other two bedrooms also have a walk in closet.  Entertain in the large backyard with room to make it your own.  Close to westside shopping and Capital Forest.
